# Text Elements
Cafeteria management for university
Keeps track of all different vendors and shops in college
Maintains all the different menu items ( including price) present in each shop
Tracks the details of shop like description, location(place in university), and 
Keeps track of all previous transactions and sales (order ID, student ID for customer)
Login page for vendors / shop owners, and students(customer)
Vendors/ Shop owners can update menu and other details
Students can place orders and the orders are notified to the respective vendors/shops.
 ^MIxcSwgj

SRS ^YVMsd7kT
